{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1265\cocoasubrtf210 \cocoascreenfonts1{\fonttbl\f0\fnil\fcharset0 LucidaGrande;} {\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;} \pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural
\f0\fs42 \cf0 Block consists of\ * ghost entries ( prev hash, next hash )\ * reorg transitions\ * new txns\ \ valid( block ) ==\ stateX( block.ghostEntries._1 ) == block.ghostEntries._2\ && stateX( block.reorgX._1 ) == block.reorgX._2}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1265\cocoasubrtf210 \cocoascreenfonts1{\fonttbl\f0\fnil\fcharset0 LucidaGrande;} {\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;} \pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural
\f0\fs30 \cf0 State transition function ( say s ) divides into two functions, \ one for application state ( say app( s ) ) and another \ for consensus management ( say cmgt( s ) ) which manages\ fees and bonds.\ \ \ def validTxn( state, stateFn, stateAccsr, e ) =\ let nState = stateFn( state, e._2 )\ ( hash( state ) == stateAccsr( e._1 )\ && hash( nState ) == stateAccsr( e._3 ), \ nState )\ \ def loopTest( testFn, acc, state, stateFn, stateAccsr, candidates ) =\ candidates match \{\ case Nil => ( true, state )\ case c :: rest => \{\ let ( cond, nState ) = testFn( state, stateFn, stateAccsr, c )\ if ( cond ) \{ \ loopTest( testFn, acc, nState, stateFn, stateAccsr, rest ) \ \}\ else ( cond, state )\ \}\ \ }

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1265\cocoasubrtf210 \cocoascreenfonts1{\fonttbl\f0\fnil\fcharset0 LucidaGrande;} {\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;} \pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural
\f0\fs34 \cf0 ... \fs30 let ( reorgCmgtCond, reorgCmgtState ) =\ loopTest( \ block.reorgX._2, \ ( e ) => validTxn( ghostState, cmgt( s ), cmgtAccsr, e )\ )\ let ( reorgAppCond, reorgAppState ) =\ loopTest( \ block.reorgX._2, \ ( e ) => validTxn( reorgInitAppState, app( s ), appAccsr, e )\ )\ let ( txnCmgtCond, txnCmgtState ) =\ loopTest( // enforcing ten fee policy of txn fees\ block.txnsX._2, \ ( e ) => validTxn( cmgtS, cmgt( s ), cmgtAccsr, e )\ )\ let ( txnAppCond, txnAppState ) =\ loopTest( \ block.txnsX._2, \ ( e ) => validTxn( appS, app( s ), appAccsr, e )\ )\ \ ( ghostCond && reorgValidity && reorgCmgtCond && reorgAppCond && txnCmgtCond && txnAppCond )\ \ }
